commit.message:
Welcome Back!

- Added icons in prep for custom drinks

Bug fixes

- Polished up the ListVIew
- Some refactoring

*Finally* fixed a stupid bug that plagued me for about 20 hours

- The homepage's ListView now actually renders items
- The reason it didn't work before was because I forgot to commit the changes in the `Write()` function to the `history.csv` file.
Even more bug fixes ... repo is now public!
Fixed a bug with dialog boxes closing abruptly

Optimized the disambiguation dialog

- A failed recognition will automatically forward to a confirmation tab on the not-yet-implemented home screen
- A perfect recognition forwards to the home screen as well, except now auto-populating the not-yet-implemented input fields
- Bug fixes, etc. Cosmetic tweaks throughout

Minor Bug and Text Fixes

- Preparing for major `Add Drink` overhaul

Added disambiguation dialog

- Majorly refactored the `Drink` class
  - Can now be de-,serialized at will

Many Changes

- Revamped UI, mostly
- Improved under-the-hood performance by a lot
- Added caffeine sources and working identification
- Other small changes and bug fixes
